# urtak-php

A PHP client library for the Urtak API.

This is very new and should be used with care.

## Versioning

We use semantic versioning with the API itself.

## Getting Started

    // Build a configuration array, more options in the docs
    $configuration = array(
      'publication_key' => 'd41d8cd98f00b204e9800998ecf8427e', 
      'api_key'         => 'e8e1b029c86b08560f77bf3c23f42707f821ef37'
    );
  
    // Instantiate an Urtak API Wrapper Object
    return new Urtak($configuration);

    // Use it! Response is json-decoded array here
    $response = urtak_api()->get_urtaks(array());

## More Info

For more information on the Urtak API:
https://developer.urtak.com/

